      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-badge fade-up">ðŸš€ 3 Core Plans Â· 5 Powerful Add-ons</div>
        <h1 class="fade-up d1">Your complete business<br />intelligence platform</h1>
        <p class="fade-up d2">
